OL,4,CBeverly Cleary, children's author
OL,5,Cbehind Ramona Quimby, dies aged 104
OL,6, Beverly Cleary, the American children's
OL,7, author who created the feisty
OL,8, characters of Ramona Quimby and Henry
OL,9, Huggins, has died at the age of 104.
OL,11,FCleary died on Thursday at her home in
OL,12,FCarmel, California, publisher
OL,13,FHarperCollins said in a statement.
OL,15,FAt a time when children's literature
OL,16,Ftold the stories of genteel English
OL,17,Fschoolchildren, she wrote about what
OL,18,Fshe called ordinary, "grubby kids".
OL,20,FHer books were set in Portland, Oregon,
OL,21,Fwhere Cleary grew up.
